  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency assistance to highly vulnerable HHs affected by Cyclone Amphan and Covid-19 in Satkhira Di</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project will support the affected population by Cyclone Amphan and COVID 19 of Satlhira district, sub-districts e.g. Kaliganj and Shymnagar. A total of 2500 households will be provided cash grant (BDT. 3000 each), hygiene kits, water points at public places, posters on COVID 19 as per WHO guidance, radio talk show highlighting safety issue on COVID 19, etc.</narrative>
  </description>
